In the penultimate episode of the season, James is joined by the unofficial mayor of Hanover and the official voice of the world's most popular football video game. Together former Hannover 96 legend Steve Cherundolo and renowned commentator Derek Rae discuss German football identity and its relationship with US soccer. This episode also includes a discussion about the best bratwurst in the Bundesliga (we cover all the important topics). Thanks for listening. If you want to get in touch then drop us a line via Twitteror Instagram.